- cs.PF (Performance) is also likely as the paper evaluates the performance impact of the proposed design on realistic use-cases. 
- cs.Distributed is another possible category as the paper discusses a one-sided communication system, which is a common topic in distributed computing. 
- cs.AR (Architecture) is a possible category as the paper describes the design of a library implementation for the proposed concepts. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed design using micro-benchmarks and a scientific application kernel.
